with onion and carrot.

125
00:08:07,230 --> 00:08:08,870
But I changed it to climbing wattle.

126
00:08:08,870 --> 00:08:10,250
It tastes quite nice.

127
00:08:11,430 --> 00:08:12,670
Try it.

128
00:08:14,870 --> 00:08:17,000
