147
00:09:37,180 --> 00:09:38,740
My dad?

148
00:09:38,900 --> 00:09:42,650
My dad was very kind.

149
00:09:42,750 --> 00:09:44,480
He was always in a good mood.

150
00:09:44,560 --> 00:09:46,600
He loved his family dearly.

151
00:09:46,730 --> 00:09:47,870
Actually,

152
00:09:47,870 --> 00:09:50,710
