161
00:10:15,350 --> 00:10:16,940
Oh, right.

162
00:10:17,030 --> 00:10:19,090
I just knew that I have a grandpa.

163
00:10:19,170 --> 00:10:21,960
I also have an uncle
whom I haven’t seen for a long time.

164
00:10:21,960 --> 00:10:24,770
