that tie you two together.

174
00:12:38,280 --> 00:12:41,700
Forgiveness is important.

175
00:12:41,780 --> 00:12:43,240
Don’t forget this.

176
00:13:20,130 --> 00:13:21,370
[Forgiveness?]

177
00:13:22,130 --> 00:13:23,260
