186
00:13:46,630 --> 00:13:49,130
[I actually want him to stay.]

187
00:13:49,190 --> 00:13:50,680
[He makes me feel safe.]

188
00:13:50,780 --> 00:13:52,510
[He makes my heart warm.]

189
00:13:53,670 --> 00:13:55,760
[I have no hidden agenda.]

190
00:13:55,990 --> 00:13:58,220
[I told him to go home.]

191
00:13:58,300 --> 00:14:00,160
[But he still insisted.]

192
