242
00:21:17,170 --> 00:21:18,750
Pharm…

243
00:21:20,950 --> 00:21:24,310
I am Pharm.

244
00:21:27,350 --> 00:21:28,410
Yes.

245
00:21:28,850 --> 00:21:30,750
You are Pharm.

246
00:21:32,990 --> 00:21:34,830
But today,

247
00:21:35,970 --> 00:21:38,250
